text: "Edging" is a 2022 song by Blink-182 and is the leading single from their ninth studio album One More Time.... It went to number 61 in the United States, number 31 in the United Kingdom, number 50 in Australia, number 18 in Japan and number 25 in Canada. It charted outside the top 40 in New Zealand. ==References== Category:2022 songs Category:Punk rock songs Category:Blink-182 songs
